#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting &spectacle;"
msgstr "&spectacle; käivitamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "&spectacle; can be started in a variety of ways, as described below:"
msgstr "&spectacle; on võimalik käivitada mitmel moel:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In the application launcher menu, &spectacle; can be found at "
#| "<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Applications</guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Graphics</"
#| "guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Screenshot Capture Utility &spectacle;</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice>"
msgid ""
"In the application launcher menu, &spectacle; can be found at "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Applications</guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Utilities</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Screenshot Capture Utility &spectacle;</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Rakenduste käivitaja menüüs leiab &spectacle; menüüst "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Rakendused</guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Graafika</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Ekraani pildistamise tööriist &spectacle;</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing the <keysym>Print Screen</keysym> button on the keyboard (often "
"labeled <keycap>PrtSc</keycap>, <keycap>PrtScn</keycap> or similar) will "
"immediately launch &spectacle;. Additionally, three more keyboard shortcuts "
"are available to take screenshots and save them in your default save folder "
"without showing the &GUI;:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Meta</keycap><keysym>Print Screen</"
"keysym></keycombo> will take a screenshot of the active window"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keysym>Print Screen</keysym></keycombo> "
"will take a screenshot of your entire desktop, &ie; all monitors"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Meta</keycap>&Shift;<keysym>Print Screen</"
"keysym></keycombo> will take a rectangular region screenshot"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can configure the default save location and filename by starting "
#| "&spectacle; normally, clicking the downward arrow beside the "
#| "<guibutton>Save &amp; Exit</guibutton> button, and selecting "
#| "<guimenuitem>Preferences</guimenuitem> from the menu."
msgid ""
"You can configure the default save location and filename by starting "
"&spectacle; normally and clicking on the <guibutton>Configure...</guibutton> "
"button, then navigating to the Save section."
msgstr ""
"Vaikimisi salvestamise asukohta ja failinime saab seadistada, kui käivitada "
"&spectacle; tavapäraselt, klõpsata allapoole näitavale noolekesele nupu "
"<guibutton>Salvesta ja välju</guibutton> kõrval ning valida menüüst "
"<guimenuitem>Eelistused</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The mini command line &krunner; (invoked with <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo>) may also be used to start "
"&spectacle;."
msgstr ""
"&spectacle; käivitamiseks saab kasutada ka mini-käsurida &krunner; (selle "
"käivitab kiirklahv <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></"
"keycombo>).."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&spectacle; can be started from the command-line. &spectacle; has an "
"extensive set of command-line options, including a background mode which can "
"be used to script the capture of screenshots without showing the &GUI; or "
"requiring user interaction."
msgstr ""
"&spectacle; on võimalik käivitada käsurealt. &spectacle; pakub laia valikut "
"käsureavõtmeid, kaasa arvatud taustal töötamise režiimi, mille abil võib "
"skriptiga lasta ekraanipilte teha ilma graafilist rakendust näitamata või "
"kasutajalt omapoolset tegevust nõudmata."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "To start &spectacle; from the command prompt, type in:"
msgstr "&spectacle; käivitamiseks käsurealt kirjuta:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "<prompt>%</prompt> <command>spectacle &amp;</command>"
msgstr "<prompt>%</prompt> <command>spectacle &amp;</command>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To view the full list of command-line options and their explanation, type in:"
msgstr "Kõigi käsureavõtmete ja nende seletuste nägemiseks kirjuta:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "<prompt>%</prompt> <command>spectacle --help</command>"
msgstr "<prompt>%</prompt> <command>spectacle --help</command>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &spectacle;"
msgstr "&spectacle; kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Once &spectacle; starts, you will see a window like the following:"
msgstr "Kui &spectacle; on käivitunud, avaneb umbes selline pilt:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "&spectacle; Main Window"
msgstr "&spectacle; peaaken"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&spectacle; grabs an image of your entire desktop immediately after it is "
"started, but before it displays itself on screen. This allows you to quickly "
"create full-desktop screenshot images."
msgstr ""
"&spectacle; võtab kogu töölauast pildi otsekohe käivitamise ajal, kuid enne "
"seda, kui ta ise ennast töölauale seab. See võimaldab kiiresti luua "
"hetktõmmiseid kogu töölauast."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The snapshot taken by &spectacle; is displayed in the preview window, which "
"is located on the left-hand side of the &spectacle; application window."
msgstr ""
"&spectacle; tehtud pilti näeb eelvaatluse sektsioonis, mis asub &spectacle; "
"akna vasakul küljel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The image can be saved by clicking on the arrow portion of the "
#| "<guibutton>Save &amp; Exit</guibutton> button, and choosing "
#| "<guimenuitem>Save As...</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
#| "&Shift;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo>) option. This opens standard save "
#| "dialog, where you can choose the filename, the folder location, and the "
#| "format that your screenshot will be saved in. You may edit the filename "
