#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To quickly save the image and quit &spectacle; press the <guibutton>Save "
#| "&amp; Exit</guibutton> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</"
