"dekoratsioonid, märkimata jätmisel aga ainult akna sisu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>Include window titlebar and borders</guilabel> option is "
