#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set a default filename for saved screenshots."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the following placeholders in the filename, which will be "
"replaced with actual text when the file is saved:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>&lt;dd&gt;</userinput>: Day"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>&lt;hh&gt;</userinput>: Hour"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>&lt;MM&gt;</userinput>: Month"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>&lt;ss&gt;</userinput>: Second"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>&lt;title&gt;</userinput>: Window title"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>&lt;yyyy&gt;</userinput>: Year (4 digit)"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>&lt;#&gt;</userinput>: Sequential number"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>&lt;mm&gt;</userinput>: Minute"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>&lt;yy&gt;</userinput>: Year (2 digit)"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can click on placeholders in the reference list below to insert them "
"into the <guilabel>Filename</guilabel> line."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a file with this name already exists, a serial number will be appended to "
"the filename. For example, if the filename is <filename>Screenshot</"
"filename>, and <filename>Screenshot.png</filename> already exists, the image "
"will be saved as <filename>Screenshot-1.png</filename>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the drop-down box next to the text field to select the default image "
"format for screenshots. See <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Image_file_formats\">Wikipedia page</ulink> for the details on the image "
"formats that are used in &spectacle;."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcuts"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This configuration page can be used to change the default shortcuts of "
"&spectacle;. It is possible to configure shortcuts for starting &spectacle; "
"and capturing different parts of your desktop."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drag and Drop"
msgstr "Lohistamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A captured image can be dragged to another application or document. If the "
"application is able to handle images, a copy of the full image is inserted "
"there."
msgstr ""
"Tehtud pildi võib lohistada mõnda teisse rakendusse või dokumenti. Kui "
"rakendus suudab pilte käsitada, lisatakse pildi täielik koopia."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you drag a screenshot into a file manager window, a dialog pops up where "
"you can edit the filename and select the image format and the file will be "
"inserted into the actual folder."
msgstr ""
"Kui lohistad pildi failihalduri aknasse, ilmub dialoog, kus saab muuta "
"failinime ja valida pildivormingu, mille järel fail lisatakse aktiivsesse "
"kataloogi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you drag the screenshot to a text box, the path to the temporary saved "
"file is inserted. This is useful for example to upload a screenshot through "
"web forms or to attach screenshots into bug reports on the <ulink url="
"\"https://bugs.kde.org/\">&kde; bugtracker</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Kui lohistad pildi tekstikasti, lisatakse salvestatud ajutise faili asukoht. "
"See on abiks näiteks pildi üleslaadimisel veebivormi kaudu või pildi "
"lisamisel veateatesse <ulink url=\"https://bugs.kde.org/\">&kde; vigade "
"jälgimise leheküljel</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This works with all clients that do not pick up the image data, but only "
"look for a &URL; in the dragged mimedata."
msgstr ""
"See toimib kõigi klientidega, mis ei võta omaks pildiandmeid, vaid otsivad "
"ainult lohistatud MIME andmete &URL;-i."

